songs.title: Pekin Jazz
songs.lyrics:
'Cause we're going to China
And we're to play
In a Holiday Inn
We're going to Spain
We're going in a trip boat
Singing away
And a lot of frat rice
We're going to eat all day
Do you want it to eat here sir or do you want it to go?
Hmm, let me see...
Are you Jamaican bro?
No
End
